# Traffic Rules Learning Platform - Complete Project Structure

## 📁 Directory Structure
```
traffic-learning-platform/
│
├── config/
│   ├── database.php          # Database configuration
│   ├── config.php             # General settings
│   └── language.php           # Language settings
│
├── includes/
│   ├── functions.php          # Helper functions
│   ├── session.php            # Session management
│   └── auth.php               # Authentication functions
│
├── classes/
│   ├── Database.php           # Database connection class
│   ├── User.php               # User management
│   ├── Subscription.php       # Subscription handling
│   ├── Lesson.php             # Lesson management
│   ├── Quiz.php               # Quiz management
│   ├── Payment.php            # Payment processing
│   └── DrivingSchool.php      # Driving school management
│
├── languages/
│   ├── en.php                 # English translations
│   └── rw.php                 # Kinyarwanda translations
│
├── assets/
│   ├── css/
│   │   ├── style.css          # Main styles
│   │   └── admin.css          # Admin styles
│   ├── js/
│   │   ├── main.js            # Main JavaScript
│   │   ├── quiz.js            # Quiz functionality
│   │   └── admin.js           # Admin functionality
│   └── images/
│       ├── logo.png
│       └── traffic-signs/     # Road sign images
│
├── public/
│   ├── index.php              # Landing page
│   ├── register.php           # Registration
│   ├── login.php              # Login
│   └── dashboard.php          # User dashboard
│
├── learner/
│   ├── dashboard.php          # Learner dashboard
│   ├── lessons.php            # View lessons
│   ├── lesson-view.php        # Single lesson view
│   ├── quizzes.php            # Practice quizzes
│   ├── mock-exam.php          # Mock exams
│   ├── progress.php           # Progress tracking
│   └── subscription.php       # Manage subscription
│
├── school/
│   ├── dashboard.php          # School dashboard
│   ├── students.php           # Manage students
│   ├── add-student.php        # Register students
│   ├── student-progress.php   # Track student progress
│   ├── analytics.php          # Performance analytics
│   └── subscription.php       # School subscription
│
├── admin/
│   ├── dashboard.php          # Admin dashboard
│   ├── users.php              # Manage users
│   ├── schools.php            # Manage schools
│   ├── lessons.php            # Manage lessons
│   ├── quizzes.php            # Manage quizzes
│   ├── payments.php           # Payment records
│   ├── analytics.php          # Platform analytics
│   └── settings.php           # System settings
│
├── api/
│   ├── payment-callback.php   # Payment gateway callbacks
│   ├── quiz-submit.php        # Quiz submission endpoint
│   └── progress-update.php    # Progress update endpoint
│
└── sql/
    └── database.sql           # Database schema
```

## 🗄️ Database Schema Overview

### Users Table
- id, email, password, user_type (learner/school/admin)
- first_name, last_name, phone
- language_preference, created_at, updated_at

### Subscriptions Table
- id, user_id, plan_type, start_date, end_date
- payment_status, amount, payment_method

### Driving Schools Table
- id, user_id, school_name, registration_number
- address, contact_person, phone, email

### School Students Table
- id, school_id, student_user_id, enrolled_at
- status (active/inactive)

### Lessons Table
- id, title_en, title_rw, content_en, content_rw
- category, order, image_url, created_at

### Quizzes Table
- id, lesson_id, title_en, title_rw
- quiz_type (practice/mock), duration_minutes

### Questions Table
- id, quiz_id, question_en, question_rw
- option_a_en, option_a_rw, option_b_en, option_b_rw
- option_c_en, option_c_rw, option_d_en, option_d_rw
- correct_answer, explanation_en, explanation_rw

### Quiz Attempts Table
- id, user_id, quiz_id, score, total_questions
- started_at, completed_at, time_taken

### Progress Tracking Table
- id, user_id, lesson_id, completed
- completion_date, time_spent

### Payments Table
- id, user_id, amount, payment_method
- transaction_id, status, created_at

